data.details: Welcome to the wet and wild world of Pumpkin Hill Creek Preserve State Park. Learn about the different methods that are used, including wetland monitoring and prescribed fire. Hands-on activities will include water conservation games, water sampling and a fire engine demonstration. This event costs $7 per person. Limited to 30 people per session.
